-- BlackBerry reaches deal to sell most of its Canadian real estate
-- By Euan Rocha
-- Fri Mar 21, 2014 08:52AM EDT
-- None



TORONTO, March 21 (Reuters) - BlackBerry Ltd <BBRY.O><BB.TO> said on Friday it has reached an agreement to sell the vast majority of its real estate holdings in Canada, as part of a plan outlined earlier this year that is aimed at bolstering the smartphone maker's balance sheet. [ID:nL2N0KV1U5]

